title: Dakine Surface Vest
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Surface Vest in Black.
Vest Features:
- 1 1/4" [ 3cm ] Closed cell foam
- Waist and seat harness compatible
- Super stretch design for freedom of movement
- Zippered front for easy on/off
- Dual sport design
